## 9. Risk Mitigation

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|--------|------------|
| Agents overwhelm plugins with updates | Medium | Use dictionary; O(1) lookup; batch updates per frame |
| Control name collisions | High | Enforce naming convention: `{agent_id}.{param}` |
| Plugins apply incorrect modulation | Medium | Validation layer; clamp values; debug logging |
| Feedback loop causes instability | High | Rate-limit feedback; add damping; simulation before deployment |
| Performance degrades with many agents | Medium | Benchmark; optimize dictionary access; consider object pools |
| Debugging complex bindings difficult | Medium | Provide UI visualization; log control flow; schema registry |

